<h2 id="frequently-used-script">Frequently Used Script</h2>

<h3 id="ffmpeg">FFmpeg</h3>

<p>Show metadata:</p>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>ffmpeg -i &lt;filename&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Show packet data:</p>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>ffprobe -show_packets &lt;filename&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Create a sine wav file:</p>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>ffmpeg -f lavfi -i "sine=frequency=441:duration=5" sine_441hz_5s.wav
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="osx">OSX</h3>

<h4 id="unloadreload-the-devices">Unload/Reload the devices</h4>

<p>For the system devices:</p>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>sudo kextunload /System/Library/Extensions/AppleHDA.kext
sudo kextload /System/Library/Extensions/AppleHDA.kext
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>For the Soundflower:</p>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>sudo kextunload -b com.Cycling74.driver.Soundflower
sudo kextload -b com.Cycling74.driver.Soundflower
</code></pre></div></div>

